Herbert Corthell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Herbert_Corthell 0 Herbert Corthell (born Joseph Bertram Corthell, January 20, 1878 – January 23, 1947) was an American stage and film actor. He was born in Boston, Massachusetts, and died in Hollywood, California.
